      that the exterior doors of Sudikoff are automatically locked after 6:00pm
      weekdays, and also every weekend and holiday. In addition, the laboratory
      doors are locked at all times. You will need your access card to pass
      through locked doors.</span><br>
    <span style="font-weight: normal;"></span>
    <h2><span style="font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Books</span></h2>
    <span style="font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;"> There is no one
      book that caters for the material in the course. &nbsp;However, we do
      recommend a book on the C language - this is a very good book:</span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
